      "Developed and maintained the e-commerce website and developed from scratch an internal cross-platform application for the company.",
    technologies: [
      TECHNOLOGIES.HTML5,
      TECHNOLOGIES.CSS,
      TECHNOLOGIES.JS,
      TECHNOLOGIES.ANGULAR,
      TECHNOLOGIES.NODEJS,
